canonical:
  title: 麟州早發
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 漏鼓逢逢報五更張旍出郭赴前程戍樓隔嶺催殘角膓斷先聞出塞聲
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 麟州早發
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 漏鼓逢逢報五更。張旍出郭赴前程。戍樓隔嶺催殘角。膓斷先聞出塞聲。
korean:
  title: 인주 조발
  author: 김극기
  language: kor
  text: |-
    누고 둥둥 오경을 알리니
    깃발 날리며 성문을 나와 길을 떠나네
    수루는 고개 너머 남은 군악을 재촉하는데
    애 끊느니 출새(出塞)의 곡조 먼저 들리네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_020_0830&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 출새(出塞)의 곡조 : '
    value: 국경으로 출병할 때에는 군악(軍樂)으로 출새곡(出塞曲)을 울린다.
english:
  title: Early Departure from Rinzhou
  author: Kim Geuk-gi
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The water clock sounds its deep tones, announcing the fifth watch of night.
    Banners unfurl as we pass through the gate, embarking on our journey.
    From the garrison tower beyond the ridge, the remnant military pipes call out,
    And my heart breaks as I hear first the "Crossing the Frontier" melody.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: '"Crossing the Frontier" (出塞) is the traditional military tune played when soldiers depart for battle at the frontier.'
